Vehement/Sun Crusher/Reflector:




Reflector and Sun Crusher came storming into the bridge.

"There are bots outside of the ship!" Sun Crusher yelled.

"I know." Vehement replied, sitting in his command chair.

"What do we do, Archbishop." Reflector replied.

"For one, we must not let them know of our numbers.  Next, we must not use 
the terms 'Omniscent One' or our titles."

"But..." 

"Do not worry, it will only be while we have visitors.  Letting them who we 
are as of yet while we don't know them would be poor strategy.  At your 
posts."

Vehement used the comm. unit built into his command chair.  "This is 
Vehement, leader of the ship before you and her crew." Vehement made a motion 
to Reflector.

On the main view screen a view of Destructor appeared.

That...KitKat said she would send people, and said she was leader of the 
Predacons.  I heard nothing of what this fool has said... he thought.

"I am pleased to hear rumors that all who live here don't go insane."
